{"tid":1827343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 咁我明白乜野叫「於家居有限度人傳人」","createTime":"2020-01-17T01:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T02:18:30.000Z","uid":96561,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38a9680401a7b04bdd8e96b696d052bf5f5ba2ea","tid":1827343,"uid":96561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"睇完熱門post<br />\n小粉紅微博冒死揭武漢緊急情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1827267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1827267</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入面提及「返屋企隔離」<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地講得出呢句說話<br />\n認真覺得班病者唔會亂咁周圍去<br />\n咁的確係有限度病埋係屋企傳比屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過你地要記得當年淘大單野<br />\n病毒經由水渠傳播<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGVchru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGVchru.png&h=7e67d05c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20030401/3206326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030401%2F3206326&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=0df2aff8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030401%2F3206326&h=01aceb4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20030401/3206326</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知呢個病毒會唔會<br />\n但希望大家做到依家可以做嘅事先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係戴口罩！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b695006f74358a45a341069015c2e5801f97bac4","tid":1827343,"uid":229127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"仲有好多人又咳又打乞嗤都唔戴口罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c497c1f38b0f7700b2600e9f58a6b0f981f050","tid":1827343,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit